# fdroidcl

> F-Droid CLI client
> More information: https://github.com/mvdan/fdroidcl

- Fetch the F-Droid index:

`fdroidcl update`

- Display info about an app:

`fdroidcl show {string value: app_id}`

- Download an APK file:

`fdroidcl download {string value: app_id}`

- Search for an app in the index:

`fdroidcl search {string value: search_pattern}`

- Install an app on a connected device:

`fdroidcl install {string value: app_id}`
